summary: Some Ambi head canons I came up
body:
Some Ambi head canons I came up

  • Amber loves it when Andi wears yellow and always pushes her to wear it more often
  • They love shopping at vintage boutiques, all the workers know them and adore them
  • They always have picnic dates and Andi brings her vintage tea set that Cece gave her
  • On their first date, Bowie gave Amber the “protective dad stare”
  • Amber gushes about Andi just a little bit too much to TJ
  • One time they went on a double date with Bex and Bowie, they went to vintage shops and listened to 80’s music in the car
  • Andi makes Amber bracelets All. The. Time.
  • When Andi and Amber told Jonah about them getting together, he laughed so much and said “wow, both my ex-girlfriends are together”
  • They also go on double dates with TJ and Cyrus
  • And on those double dates, they always watch “love, Simon” because it’s a classic
  • Andi and Amber fangirl about Billie Eilish
  • Amber is a hardcore Billie Eilish stan so she always sings to Andi (Amber also playa ukelele)
  • Did I mention that Andi taught Amber how to make dandelion flower crowns? No? Well, she did that too
  • They had their first kiss on a Ferris wheel
  • One day when they were having a double date with tyrus, they went on canoes and TJ kept on singing “kiss the girl”
